 dried chromium.</i>

00:12:04.923 --> 00:12:09.061
<i> Outside, the kids are playing
 a gleeful game of cricket,</i>

00:12:09.061 --> 00:12:10.428
<i> the national sport,</i>

00:12:10.428 --> 00:12:12.630
<i> and they are playing
 on a field of</i>

00:12:12.630 --> 00:12:16.001
