 people come to die.</i>

00:14:57.095 --> 00:14:58.964
<i> All this work
 and a bunch of essays I wrote</i>

00:14:58.964 --> 00:15:00.966
<i> were published on
the National Geographic magazine</i>

00:15:00.966 --> 00:15:02.534
<i> 'Proof' blog recently.</i>

00:15:02.534 --> 00:15:04.370
<i> I'm just going to read you
 the opening sentence</i>

00:15:04.370 --> 00:15:08.907
<i> of the blog that went
 with the Varanasi story.</i>

00:15:08.907 --> 00:15:10.942
<i> "When you step off
 a wooden boat</i>

00:15:10.942 --> 00:15:12.510
<i> onto the banks
 of the burning ghat</i>

00:15:12.510 --> 00:15:14.746
<i>in the oldest of India's cities</i>

00:15:14.746 --> 00:15:17.816
<i> and you weave through a maze
 of funeral pyres hissing,</i>

00:15:17.816 --> 00:15:19.818
<i> steaming and
