00:15:19.818 --> 00:15:21.653
<i> into the inky night</i>

00:15:21.653 --> 00:15:24.022
<i> and you feel
 the metronome clang of bells</i>

00:15:24.022 --> 00:15:27.592
<i> vibrating inside your chest
and a wave of furnace-like heat</i>

