00:18:39.117 --> 00:18:40.518
<i> somebody washing their hair,</i>

00:18:40.518 --> 00:18:42.654
<i> somebody collecting
 sacred Gangajal,</i>

00:18:42.654 --> 00:18:45.657
<i> they are going to bring back
 to their village.</i>

00:18:45.657 --> 00:18:48.593
Back to our water data,

00:18:48.593 --> 00:18:50.829
this whole concept of
the river coming back to life

00:18:50.829 --> 00:18:52.464
is interesting because

00:18:52.464 --> 00:18:54.766
there's a thing... they are
calling it the X-factor.

00:18:54.766 --> 00:18:58.103
They believe it is related to
bacteriophages, that...

00:18:58.103 --> 00:19:00.238
if all these people come
into the river everyday,

00:19:00.238 --> 00:19:02.073
and they are treating it
like a bathroom,

00:19:02.073 --> 00:19:03.675
why are they not
getting sicker?

00:19:03.675 --> 00:19:05.543
Well, the oxygen level
does return

00:19:05.543 --> 00:19:07.646
and the oxygen
actually helps to...

00:19:07.646 --> 00:19:10.148
to support
these bacteriophages,

00:19:10.148 --> 00:19:11.583
which eat bacteria.

00:19:11.583 --> 00:19:13.051
And that's one theory why

00:19:13.051 --> 00:19:16.121
these epidemics, cholera
epidemics haven't occurred

00:19:16.121 --> 00:19:17.488
with one million people

00:19:17.488 --> 00:19:19.324
coming for certain festivals
and what not.

00:19:19.324 --> 00:19:21.760
So, there is some element of
the curative power

00:19:21.760 --> 00:19:23.095
to this river.

00:19:23.095 --> 00:19:26.264
And after six weeks,

00:19:26.264 --> 00:19:30.435
travelling 1550 miles,
roughly three vertical miles,

00:19:30.435 --> 00:19:32.737
in theory,
we were free of sin because,

00:19:32.737 --> 00:19:34.239
believe me, I did wade,

00:19:34.239 --> 00:19:36.675
walk, swim, fall in

00:19:36.675 --> 00:19:40.412
the Ganges
many times on this trip.

00:19:40.412 --> 00:19:43.081
Yes, I was free of sin
and I was free of 35 pounds.

00:19:43.081 --> 00:19:45.284
I lost a bit of weight.

00:19:45.284 --> 00:19:46.818
It is a good
weight loss program.

